inanced (D/E 0.03\u00d7).","Profit up 25% YoY (latest TTM) and accelerating."],"key_risks":["Below its 200-day average (-19%) \u2014 downtrend.","39% below its 52-week high.","In a deep drawdown (-39% from its peak)."],"monitor_next":["Next quarterly results (board-meeting date is an MVP-2 placeholder).","Re-rating toward / away from its median P/E (20.1\u00d7).","Relative-strength inflection vs its sector index.","Promoter pledge / institutional-holding changes next quarter."],"caveats":["Thinly traded \u2014 median ~\u20b90.25 cr/day (< \u20b91 cr); signals/exits may slip.","corporate-action gaps, illiquid names, or a short listing history can distort returns/DMA/RS."],"confidence":"medium","disclaimer":"Diagnostics only \u2014 a structured reading of price behaviour, business fundamentals, valuation and ownership for your OWN judgement. This is NOT a buy/sell/hold recommendation.","method":"Each dimension is a transparent points tally of the named signals listed beneath it \u2014 open a dimension to see the exact signals that fired and its rule. Verdict = positive at +2 or more / negative at \u22122 or less for Market, Business and Valuation; \u00b11 for Ownership. A 'positive' valuation means the multiple looks supportive vs the stock's OWN history \u2014 never a buy call."},"data_quality":{"price_asof":"2026-07-02","fundamentals_fetched":"2026-06-20","has_fundamentals":true,"has_shareholding":true,"liquidity_warning":"Thinly traded \u2014 median ~\u20b90.25 cr/day (< \u20b91 cr); signals/exits may slip.","note":"Market data is daily and current; fundamentals & shareholding are as of the last cached Screener fetch (quarterly/annual). Confidence is lower for thin or short-history names."}}